The paper also involves optimization problems related to graphs and communication costs, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper mentions symmetric key cryptography, which is a topic related to cs.IT (Information Theory).
